  2019,"10",/general-conference/2019/10/11holland,Elder Jeffrey R. Holland,31,The region in upstate New York near Palmyra was often referred to as “the burned-over district” due to the religious zeal that regularly swept through those small communities.
  2019,"10",/general-conference/2019/10/11holland,Elder Jeffrey R. Holland,32,"Joseph Smith—History 1:13."
