  2019,"10",/general-conference/2019/10/17oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,36,"SeeTeachings of Presidents of the Church: Joseph Smith(2007), 175."
  2019,"10",/general-conference/2019/10/17oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,37,"History of the Church,6:52; included inTeachings of the Prophet Joseph Smith,326; often quoted, as in Henry B. Eyring,To Draw Closer to God(1997), 122; see alsoTeachings of Presidents of the Church: Brigham Young(1997), chapter 38, “The Spirit World.”"
