  2019,"10",/general-conference/2019/10/31aburto,Reyna I. Aburto,39,Knowing how to recognize signs and symptoms in ourselves and others can be helpful. We can also learn to detect inaccurate or unhealthy thinking patterns and how to replace them with more accurate and healthier ones.
  2019,"10",/general-conference/2019/10/31aburto,Reyna I. Aburto,40,Depression can also result from positive life changes—such as the birth of a child or a new job—and can occur when things are good in a person’s life.
