  2019,"10",/general-conference/2019/10/41gong,Elder Gerrit W. Gong,57,"SeeDoctrine and Covenants 128:8; see alsoExodus 19:5–6;Doctrine and Covenants 84:40. Those who worthily keep covenants become a precious treasure, a kingdom of priests, a holy nation. Covenants sanctify. Those who keep covenants become sanctified to the Lord."
