  2019,"10",/general-conference/2019/10/46nelson,President Russell M. Nelson,55,"See “Worldwide Displacement Tops 70 Million, UN Refugee Chief Urges Greater Solidarity in Response,” United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees website, June 19, 2019, unhcr.org/en-us."
  2019,"10",/general-conference/2019/10/46nelson,President Russell M. Nelson,56,"For additional information on the Church’s charitable efforts, please seeChurchofJesusChrist.org/topics/welfare;LatterDaySaintCharities.org;facebook.com/LatterDaySaintCharities;JustServe.org."
